<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar'); -%>

        <section>
            <div class="carts-craft-about-banner section-gap">
                <img src="/images/service-banner.png" alt="About Banner">
                <h1>careers</h1>
            </div>
        </section>


        <section class="career-section section-gap">
            <div class="career-section__grid ecommerce-container">
                <div class="career-section__grid-img">
                    <img src="/images/project-manager.png" alt="">
                    <!-- <div class="border"></div> -->
                </div>
                <div class="career-section__grid-content">
                    <h2>Job Title: Digital Marketing Specialist</h2>
                    <h6>Full Time</h6>
                    <p><strong>Description: </strong> We are seeking a talented Digital Marketing Specialist to join our
                        team. In this role, you will be responsible for developing and executing digital marketing
                        strategies to increase our online presence and drive customer engagement.</p>
                    <p>You will manage paid advertising campaigns, analyze data to refine marketing efforts, and work
                        closely with our content and design teams to create compelling online marketing materials. If
                        you are passionate about digital marketing, data-driven decision-making, and have a creative
                        flair, we'd love to hear from you.</p>
                    <div class="career-section__grid-content-btn">
                        <span class="career-button">Location: Thane</span>
                        <a href="/careers/digital-marketing-specialist" class="career-button">Explore</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="career-section section-gap">
            <div class="career-section__grid ecommerce-container">
                <div class="career-section__grid-content">
                    <h2>E-commerce Account Manager</h2>
                    <h6>Part Time</h6>
                    <p>Are you a detail-oriented professional with a passion for e-commerce? We are looking for an
                        E-commerce Account Manager to oversee and optimize our online sales channels.</p>
                    <p>Your responsibilities will include managing e-commerce platform accounts, analyzing sales data,
                        coordinating product listings, and implementing strategies to enhance the customer shopping
                        experience. If you have a strong background in e-commerce, excellent communication skills, and a
                        knack for problem-solving, we want to talk to you.</p>
                    <div class="career-section__grid-content-btn">
                        <span class="career-button">Location: Thane</span>
                        <a href="/careers/ecommerce-account-manager" class="career-button">Explore</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="career-section__grid-img-right">
                    <img src="/images/project-manager.png" alt="" loading="lazy">
                    <div class="border-right"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="career-section section-gap">
            <div class="career-section__grid ecommerce-container">
                <div class="career-section__grid-img">
                    <img src="/images/project-manager.png" alt="">
                    <!-- <div class="border"></div> -->
                </div>
                <div class="career-section__grid-content">
                    <h2>Web Developer</h2>
                    <h6>Full Time</h6>
                    <p><strong>Description: </strong>We are in search of a skilled Web Developer to join our dynamic
                        team. As a Web Developer, you will play a key role in building and maintaining our company's
                        online presence. Your responsibilities will include coding, designing, and modifying websites to
                        meet user requirements and optimizing website performance. </p>
                    <p>You'll collaborate with our design and marketing teams to create user-friendly web interfaces and
                        ensure a seamless user experience. If you are proficient in web development, have an eye for
                        detail, and are passionate about creating exceptional online experiences, we encourage you to
                        apply.</p>
                    <div class="career-section__grid-content-btn">
                        <span class="career-button">Location: Thane</span>
                        <a href="/careers/web-developer" class="career-button">Explore</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

